title: K-pop New Year's Concert
description: Right after midnight, the most famous K-pop band of the moment is going to entertain the gathering with their cool songs, and these girls can’t wait to see the BTS boys performing. They've got the tickets, and they just need the right looks, and here is where you can help them out! Get ready to prove your stylist skills, ladies, while playing the K-pop New Year’s Concert dress up game for girls online!
